metadata.description:
The model renders different shapes separated by drawing style but combined by flowfield. Try to look closely: there might be shapes that are imperceptible at first sight. 

There are several traits:
- 20 color palettes;
- 9 compositions (5 fixed and 1 randomly generated);
- 6 drawing scales;
- Infinite patterns.

Press 's' to save .png with resolution 2000px * 2000px.

Renders fastest in Chrome browser.

Made with p5js, math and love by @ivposure
